{"id": 7144, "title": "Ticket #7144: Dedicated scheduler should not use UDP to release claims on startds", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe dedicated scheduler uses UDP to release the claims it has on startds when shutting down.  Many startds today do not have UDP ports, and the serial schedd does not use UDP by deafult for this.  This ticket will change the shutdown logic to always use TCP to release any claims.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2019-Aug-05 16:40:17 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>Code Review</strong>\n\n<p>These changes look good.</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Aug-06 08:16</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/325f09f2776df953ac93f9890846f4b3703ef2e7\">[57603]</a></span>: Document <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7144\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7144'); return false;\" title=\"Dedicated scheduler should not use UDP to release claims on startds\">#7144</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Jul-10 09:00</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/e2e2c54ad11306d17c091d850ada884056fc4ac4\">[57363]</a></span>: Always use TCP to release claims from the dedicated scheduler <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7144\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7144'); return false;\" title=\"Dedicated scheduler shou